	html := `<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Terms of Service - Mewify</title><style>body{font-family:-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;color:#333;line-height:1.6}h1{color:#3B82F6}h2{color:#2563EB;margin-top:30px}</style></head><body><h1>Terms of Service</h1><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 7, 2026</p><p>By using Mewify, you agree to these Terms of Service.</p><h2>Use of Service</h2><p>Mewify provides AI-powered facial analysis, mewing tracking, and glow plan recommendations. Results are for entertainment and informational purposes only, not medical advice. You must be at least 13 years old.</p><h2>Account Responsibilities</h2><ul><li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account.</li><li>You must provide accurate information when creating an account.</li><li>You must not use the service for any illegal purposes.</li></ul><h2>Subscriptions</h2><ul><li>Premium features require a paid subscription.</li><li>Subscriptions are billed through Apple's App Store.</li><li>You can cancel anytime through your Apple ID settings.</li><li>Refunds are handled by Apple according to their refund policy.</li></ul><h2>Content Guidelines</h2><ul><li>You must not upload inappropriate or illegal content.</li><li>We reserve the right to remove content that violates our guidelines.</li></ul><h2>Limitation of Liability</h2><p>Mewify is provided "as is" without warranties. AI analysis results are for entertainment only and should not be considered medical or professional advice.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>For questions, contact us at: <strong>ahmetk3436@gmail.com</strong></p></body></html>`
